        {
            "id": 6439322,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 微軟(MSFT-US)大跌5.04%，報403.07美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>微軟(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)截至台北時間30日22:06股價下跌21.39美元，報403.07美元，跌幅5.04%，成交量13,970,242（股），盤中最高價414.42美元、最低價403.07美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.84%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.21%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.64%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>微軟(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.95%</li> <li>近 1 月：+18.97%</li> <li>近 3 月：-2.09%</li> <li>近 6 月：-21.62%</li> <li>今年以來：-12.23%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6439322",
